[{"id":824535,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1635652519","description":"<p>最近 3 个月用 MacBook Air M1 过程中，遇到 3 次死机的情况了，都是强制关机解决，而且还造成部分软件编辑中的内容丢失\n原来公司配的 ThinkPad 在使用的几年内几乎没有遇到死机的情况</p>\n<p>所以才会有 macOS 不如 Windows 稳定的感受，当然这不是严谨的对比，像 ThinkPad 由于是公司电脑装也仅安装办公所需软件</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824535","replies":114,"created_ts":1640521404,"created":"20:23:24","title":"从最近的使用感受来看， macOS 似乎不如 Windows 稳定","author":"lj0014","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lj0014","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2127/8bab/15178_mini.png?m=1392785642"},{"id":824492,"node":"电动汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ev","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_mini.png?m=1590433590","description":"<p>有没有搞电动汽车的？国产和特斯拉的差距有多大？<br/>感觉国产车只能靠外围，换壳，换电池，双摄改三射，100 万像素改 200 万，只换不修等类似卖手机的操作来吸引眼球，寻找卖点</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824492","replies":113,"created_ts":1640502608,"created":"15:10:08","title":"有没有搞电动汽车的？国产和特斯拉的差距有多大？","author":"blufaux","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/blufaux","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/540af5eccc747a348fb0337ef42a3623?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":824483,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984","description":"<h2>软考干啥？</h2>\n<p>评职称啊，一般互联网人 35 岁以后该干嘛？进公家单位！进去了就得遵守另一套规则了，不是技术多 6 工资多高，得看工龄和职称！！</p>\n<p>当然，工龄没办法帮你们了。</p>\n<p>职称就可以提前准备了，计算机专业以考代评，考到证了，就约等于有了职称！ so ，互联网官方认证，软考（中国计算机技术职业资格网）</p>\n<h2>教程，视频，资源</h2>\n<p>地址： <a href=\"https://pan.htm.fun/%E8%BD%AF%E8%80%83%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://pan.htm.fun/软考目录</a></p>\n<p>可在线看。\n目前已经有很多了，但是还是有一些目录是空的，还在整理中...</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824483","replies":112,"created_ts":1640500210,"created":"14:30:10","title":"互联网人得考个软考，全套资料，我自己网上收集整理的，中级高级都有，初级太智障了没存","author":"stayma","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/stayma","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/64337665631783c1b73030a1681fd289?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":824561,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984","description":"好像是得先登陆这个 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://filehelper.weixin.qq.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://filehelper.weixin.qq.com</a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824561","replies":78,"created_ts":1640529245,"created":"22:34:05","title":"喜大普奔，网页版 WeChat 又能登陆了","author":"des","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/des","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7ca1/5681/88909_mini.png?m=1574917080"},{"id":824502,"node":"教育","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/edu","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0690/59b7/126_mini.png?m=1371465007","description":"<ul>\n<li>本人有个弟弟，初中不好好读书，中考之后，分数太低，没有公办的学校可读，平时也没啥兴趣爱好，请问大家的建议，还有其他的法子吗？</li>\n</ul>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824502","replies":78,"created_ts":1640506926,"created":"16:22:06","title":"学习不好的初中生","author":"ha2ha","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ha2ha","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea73/8b59/561979_mini.png?m=1640073432"},{"id":824516,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1635652519","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824516","replies":62,"created_ts":1640512855,"created":"18:00:55","title":"macOS 的截图快捷键非常晦涩难懂，有什么历史渊源吗？","author":"szzhiyang","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/szzhiyang","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a14d/4c46/317258_mini.png?m=1640512548"},{"id":824506,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/aa5204E3b.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824506","replies":59,"created_ts":1640508331,"created":"16:45:31","title":"继 iMessage，共享相册，日历后，家庭也遭殃了😂","author":"chiaf","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/chiaf","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b0b6/208d/209640_mini.png?m=1487059376"},{"id":824517,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984","description":"<p>今天进入微云看了下，已经按照政策实行免费用户不限速上下载服务了。测试了一下，速度还算不错。我选择微云的原因主要有这几个:1.最主要的方面，我觉得他轻。与繁杂的百度网盘比起来，微云几乎所有的操作都可以在网页上完成，不需要强制使用客户端，而且对文件大小不作限制。2.可以支持同步助手 3.与 QQ/微信互联，可以直接将别人发送的文件转存到网盘里 4.几乎不封资源，也不会出现分享链接失效的情况 5.价格方面普通会员仅需 10 元就可以获得 3T 空间，升级到高等级还有更多，比别的网盘便宜不少。</p>\n<p>//我是微云几年的老用户，绝对没有给腾讯打广告的意思，只是真心觉得不错，有不同意见可以在下面留言。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824517","replies":56,"created_ts":1640513546,"created":"18:12:26","title":"微云或许是最香的网盘","author":"zbzzh","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zbzzh","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a9af/f784/550728_mini.png?m=1626135091"},{"id":824480,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1635654575","description":"<p>前两天 tomcat 启动慢的原因 百思不得其解 最后发现 是因为 连局域网的就很慢, 在本机的虚拟机里装了数据库就正常了 (oracle)\n结果 m1 下装 armwin11  oeacle xe11g 都能装 , sqlserver 却装不了....微软自家产品自家系统 这都搞不定的么?</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824480","replies":51,"created_ts":1640499191,"created":"14:13:11","title":"盖了老帽儿了.m1 芯片 居然装不了 sqlserver","author":"helee9199","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/helee9199","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5a82249defccd648ef6d961847c0480c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":824473,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"<p>家里宽带带宽应该有 30m 。用迅雷资源也很快。但是微信迁移（ iPhone11 to pc ）聊天记录只有几百 k 的速度，真的好慢。<br/><br/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824473","replies":51,"created_ts":1640493391,"created":"12:36:31","title":"微信聊天记录迁移怎么就这么慢。","author":"TmacV2","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/TmacV2","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/063d/bc95/154134_mini.png?m=1451954419"},{"id":824475,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1635654575","description":"<p>公司人越来越多，加班反而也多了。这一定是 PHP 的原因。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824475","replies":41,"created_ts":1640495456,"created":"13:10:56","title":"有没有 30 天精通 golang 的教程？","author":"richangfan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/richangfan","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a03e1fcf593320459b61bab844e1fa80?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":824463,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984","description":"<p>用过不少拦截软件，adbyby ，koolproxy ，adguardhome ，ublock ，x 浏览器自带的拦截，via 浏览器。</p>\n<p>拦截规则也有很多：easy ，cjx ，Fanboy ，yhosts ，Halflife 合成的等等。</p>\n<p>最后的经验是：订阅的越多，问题越多（不是效率问题），是误拦截越多（这个有时真的很烦人）。</p>\n<p>现在只用 2 个规则：easylist 和 easylist china 。\n够用，稳定，放心，没遇到过误拦截。</p>\n<p>一点经验分析，也欢迎讨论</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824463","replies":31,"created_ts":1640488038,"created":"11:07:18","title":"拦截规则还真不能随意订阅","author":"brMu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/brMu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8af27915861d7372cf289ba0dca4836f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":824457,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/824457","replies":27,"created_ts":1640479081,"created":"08:38:01","title":"各位今年回老家过年吗？","author":"Zink99","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zink99","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbf8/40d8/380588_mini.png?m=1588839478"}]